  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Tracker<P,T extends Tracker.Item<?,?,P>>
    General interface to define an object shape tracker and propagate object's Semantics.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SemanticItem
    A tracking Item based Tracker.ShapeItem and aMOR semantic mapping library.
    ShapeTracker
    A Tracker implementation for MORPrimitive semantic objects and SemanticItem Item description.
    Tracker.CastMappingTry
    The Collection<? extends {T, P}> casting helper.
    Tracker.Item<S,I,P>
    The base item that defines the elements of the tracking set, managed by a Tracker.

    Tracker.UpdatingState
    The changing state during a manipulation on the tracking set (see: Tracker).
